{{#presenter-container class="flex layout-column" as |container|}}
  {{#container.header}}
    {{#paper-toolbar-tools}}
      {{paper-button iconButton=true class="hidden"}}
      <h2 class="flex">S8-C recommender engine</h2>
      <span>1/4</span>
      {{application-menu}}
      {{#paper-button iconButton=true onClick=(action "proceed")}}
        {{paper-icon "arrow_forward"}}
      {{/paper-button}}
    {{/paper-toolbar-tools}}
  {{/container.header}}

  {{#container.content class="flex layout-column min-width-70" as |card|}}
    {{#card.content class="flex layout-column layout-gt-xs-row card-content"}}

      <div class="md-padding flex flex-xs-40" style="text-align:center;position: relative;background: #EEE;">
        <img src="/dynamic-consent/assets/images/sightsee_1.jpg" class="layout-fill" style="width:100%;height:100%; position: absolute;top:0;left:0;"/>
      </div>

      <div class="flex layout-column margin-auto">
        <div class="md-padding">
          Thank your for choosing our application which will provide you with customized sightseeing recommendations based on your personal interests and your location.
        </div>

        <div class="md-padding">
          The list of events is filtered against preferences that the application will discover about you over time, if you so desire.
          To provide that service, the application needs access to your current location. This is entirely under your control and there will be hidden data collection at no time.
        </div>

        <div class="md-padding">
          Starting on the next screen, we'll walk you through the installation process to get the most out of our recommendations.
        </div>
      </div>

    {{/card.content}}

  {{/container.content}}

{{/presenter-container}}